      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="0034_FL81799699"/><hi rend="pre-print">Dr. Arthur Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb168815">Wien XVIII. Sternwartestrasse 71</rs></hi></addrLine></address><address><addrLine>Herrn</addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">Dr. Stefan Zweig</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb58">Wien VIII</rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb249577"><hi rend="latintype">Kochgasse 8</hi></rs>.</addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="0035_FL81799599"/><date>Montag</date></dateline><salute>lieber Herr Doctor,</salute></opener><p>wir denken <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L03794-1"/>heute im <rs type="place" ref="#pmb74">Türken<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chanzpark</rs><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L03794-1"><ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" target="1911-06-12" subtype="See"/>.</note> zu
               nachtmahlen, nach <time>½ 9</time>. We<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c> wir Sie dort<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehen<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ollten, würd es uns<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehr freuen. Ganz unverbindlich. Antwort überflü<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ig</p><closer>Herzlich grüß<unclear>end</unclear> Ihr <signed>A. S.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
